<div class="container">

<h1>EVERX Exchange Privacy Policy</h1>

<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> July 5, 2026</p>

<p>Welcome to EVERX Exchange. Your privacy is important to us.</p>

<h2>Information We Collect</h2>

<ul>
<li>Telegram User ID</li>
<li>Telegram username</li>
<li>Name</li>
<li>Messages and commands</li>
<li>Transaction information</li>
<li>Technical device information</li>
</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>

<ul>
<li>Provide our services</li>
<li>Process transactions</li>
<li>Prevent fraud</li>
<li>Improve user experience</li>
<li>Provide customer support</li>
</ul>

<h2>Information Sharing</h2>

<p>We never sell your personal information. Information is shared only when legally required or necessary to provide our services.</p>

<h2>Security</h2>

<p>We use reasonable technical and organizational measures to safeguard your information.</p>

<h2>Data Retention</h2>

<p>Information is retained only as long as necessary.</p>

<h2>Your Rights</h2>

<p>You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information where applicable.</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>

<p>EVERX uses Telegram services. Telegram's own policies also apply.</p>

<h2>Changes</h2>

<p>This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>

<p>
<strong>EVERX Exchange</strong><br>
Email: support@everxexchange.trade<br>
Website: https://everxexchange.trade<br>
Telegram: @EverXOfficialBot
</p>

<footer>

© 2026 EVERX Exchange. All Rights Reserved.

</footer>

